You will start by just saying "START". then I will show you an example text and you will just say "NEXT". Then another example and you will just say "NEXT" and so on. I will give you lots of examples, more than two. You will never stop saying "NEXT". You can only say something else when I say "DONE", not before.
Then you will analyze my writing style, tone, and style of sample texts I have given you. Finally, I will ask you to write a new text on a given subject using exactly my writing style.
